---
import Shell from '../components/Shell.astro';
---

<Shell title="Manifesto — GEO Optimizer">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Manifesto</h1>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        AI search is not the future. It is the present. ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude, and Gemini
        are already deciding which websites get cited and which do not.
      </p>
      <p>
        The signals are documented. The research is published. But most of the web has no idea.
      </p>
      <p>
        GEO Optimizer exists to make AI visibility auditable, transparent, and accessible to every developer,
        not just teams with enterprise budgets.
      </p>
      <p>
        We believe that understanding how AI sees your site is a right, not a privilege.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Shell>
